Reviews.Title: happy to have found these
Reviews.Author: LINDA M "quimbee"
Reviews.Content: It is nice to be able to find these for my p -touch. I am happy that I have them because you never know when they may not be available

Reviews.Title: Wish I had order something with black type
Reviews.Author: AKAK
Reviews.Content: I'm gluten intolerant so I label peanut butter, jam, etc so that no one contaminates them.  I love the color but the type doesn't show up as much as I would have liked.

Reviews.Title: P-Touch User
Reviews.Author: Amazon Reviewer "David"
Reviews.Content: Got to use with our Brother P-Touch.  Works as advertised and much cheaper than those available at local stationary store.

Reviews.Title: Love it
Reviews.Author: Billie Anthony
Reviews.Content: I love this tape. The white print on pink is fun. It has been instrumental in helping me get organized. I use it on many things from file folders to cups (so we know who's glass is who's).

Reviews.Title: Cannot Complain!!
Reviews.Author: Kristen E.
Reviews.Content: Package came in timely manner, not 1 problem with this transaction!!! Great Product & Great Service!!!! I own my own business & all the office supplies I use this product saves me so much money!! Thank You So Much!!!!

Reviews.Title: Brother's tape
Reviews.Author: W. Teo
Reviews.Content: I thought the red color print with white background would stand out.Well, no.  Stick to the black print; it looks much better.Nothing wrong with the tape, just the color.
